'''ketone'''
#{{chemistry}} A homologous series of organic molecules whose funtional group is an oxygen atom joined to a carbon atom - a double bond - in a carbon-hydrogen based molecule.
 
====Examples====
*[[acetone]] R<sub>1</sub> = R<sub>2</sub> = CH<sub>3</sub>
*[[methyl ethyl ketone]] R<sub>1</sub> = CH<sub>3</sub>, R<sub>2</sub> = C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>
*[[camphor]] C₁₀H₁₇O

